<p>​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​<strong><img src="../images/transformation-home-video.jpg" alt="Transformation" width="300" height="200" class="right border" />About. </strong>This website is a collaboration of the <strong><a href="http://mchwdc.unc.edu/" target="_blank">National Maternal and Child Health Workforce Development Center</a></strong> at UNC Chapel Hill  and the MCH Navigator; it serves as a repository  for <strong><em>universal training resources/online learning materials</em></strong> in support of the Center's cores and activities. </p>
